## Checklist before delivering any copy

- [ ] Read aloud in pt-BR — sounds natural?
- [ ] Mobile test — text too long for small screens?
- [ ] Works for any tenant name (no hardcoded dealership names)?
- [ ] Module-gated states written if feature has a paid tier?
- [ ] Same term used consistently with existing glossary?
- [ ] Error messages explain what happened AND what to do?

